milestones.description: Fraser Watts and Majid Haq's 99-run partnership is SCOT's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 47 between Fraser Watts and Poonia
Hamilton has broken the record for most sixes (5) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Paul Hoffmann's 4
Poonia has broken the record for most ducks (4) in ODIs for SCOT, going past John Blain's 3
This is the highest match aggregate (512) involving teams Kenya & Scotland in ODIs
Kenya's 7-run win against Scotland is the smallest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 28-run win against Bangladesh
